mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "From the Floor", "Square Dance Date Book", "On the Record", "As I See It", "Fun for Everyone", "Square Dancers Help Open Toronto's Spectacular City Hall", "The Dancer's Walkthru", "Vox Saltator", "This Was The Weekend That Was", "Style Series: Who's on First?", "Memories of Square Dancing", "National Convention News", "Round the Outside Ring", "Sets in Order Workshop", "Caller of the Month: Dub & Zelma McDaniel", "Paging the Roundancers: Blackie & Dottie Heatwole", and "Experimental Lab: Rip the Line".
